OL,3,CMan with frozen windscreen in
OL,4,CDumfries given 12 month driving ban
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fdangerous driving in Dumfries after
OL,8,Fhe was stopped on the A701 in a van
OL,9,Fwith a frozen windscreen and windows.
OL,11,FDavid Hyslop, 54, was driving with a
OL,12,Fvery limited view of the road when he
OL,13,Fwas charged with road traffic
OL,14,Foffences in December 2022.
OL,16,FHe was convicted following a trial at
OL,17,FDumfries Sheriff Court on Wednesday,
OL,18,F22 November, 2023, receiving a 12
OL,19,Fmonth driving disqualification and a
OL,20,F#500 fine.
